                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When the accursed forge-spurned critically hits a target with its <em>soul chain</em>, the chain leeches away a portion of the target's soul. The target must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"divine,necromancy\" data-pf2-label=\"Soul Siphon DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"36\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is drained 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 2} from the pain.</p>\n</div>"
